-- ** Thief Guild Help ** --
 
During your membership, you will learn the following talents:

Basic Communications:
gtell <message>, gmote <message>

Information Commands:
thelp - this command (duh)
powers - Gives a list of talents and their costs with Glevel requirements.
levels - Monetary breakdown of costs for Glevel.

Help files are available for the following skills:

Roll corpse, Steal, Money, Scout, Trick, Palm, Silent, Trap, Shadow, Stab,
Peek, Pick, Squint, Hide, Circle, Plant, Fasttalk, Conceal, Unhide, Sewers,
and Breakin.
 
For help on any specific ability, type thelp <ability>

